These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk, juice, coffee
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, japanese, colombian, turkish
1. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
2. the turkish is on the left or right of the chinese##3
3. the chinese is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
5. the chinese is the person drinking milk##1
6. the person drinking juice is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | mirinda | milk  | juice |
| Nationality   | colombian | turkish      | chinese | japanese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, mexican, german, british
4 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, cat, mouse
1. the mexican is between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the mouse##2
2. the british is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the british##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality   | british | german | mexican   | polish |
| Pet           | cat      | hamster    | hedgehog | mouse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, zucchini, papaya, tomato
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, airplane, motorbike, ship
1. the person eating zucchini is the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
4. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
5. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
6. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | zucchini | eggplant | papaya     | tomato |
| Transport   | airplane  | ship   | motorbike | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, chess, video-games, puzzles
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, thriller, disaster, superhero
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
5. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | video-games | magic-tricks | chess | puzzles |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | disaster     | thriller    | mystery       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, carrot, broccoli, pumpkin
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, adventure, comedy, romance
1. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
2. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
3. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the left of the person eating lettuce##5
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
6. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Food          | broccoli | pumpkin   | lettuce   | carrot    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | romance | thriller | comedy |

