2. the software-developer is somewhere to the left of the british##5
3. the british is between the dressmaker and the italian##2
4. the coach is on the right of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Job           | software-developer | entrepreneur | dressmaker | coach |
| Nationality   | italian        | british     | polish       | spanish   |

