.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, reggae, rock, country
4 different pets are kept: pony, goat, lizard, ferret
1. the owner of the goat is the fan of country##1
2. the fan of classical is between the fan of reggae and the owner of the lizard##2
3. the owner of the pony is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the fan of classical##5
5. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
6. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | classical  | rock  | country   |
| Pet           | ferret  | pony | lizard | goat |

