2. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the teacher##5
3. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
4. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating onion##1
5. the teacher is somewhere to the left of the videographer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
