.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, soy-milk, water
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, grapes, lettuce, plum
1. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person eating plum##5
5. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the right of the person eating raspberry##5
6. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating lettuce##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | juice | soy-milk | water   | mirinda |
| Food       | raspberry       | lettuce   | plum | grapes |

