.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, milk, juice, coffee
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, rugby, snowboarding, climbing
1. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
2. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
3. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
4. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
5. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | milk | juice       | soy-milk   | coffee        |
| Sport      | rugby  | climbing | sailing | snowboarding |

