.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, writing, rock-climbing, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, sailing, skateboarding, surfing
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
5. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | skydiving | writing   | rock-climbing | dancing     |
| Sport   | sailing     | ice-hockey | skateboarding  | surfing |

