.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, disaster, zombie, thriller
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, sailing, badminton, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
4. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching zombie movies##5
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | zombie        | thriller        | disaster |
| Sport         | badminton  | surfing | handball | sailing |

