.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, hot-chocolate, coffee
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, jazz, r&b, blues
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the fan of blues##1
4. the fan of house is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking soy-milk and the fan of jazz##2
7. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | hot-chocolate  | 7up      | coffee       |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | blues | jazz | house |

