.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, australian, brazilian, indonesian
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, scooter, snowmobile, trike
1. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
2. the brazilian is the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the russian##5
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | russian     | australian | indonesian | brazilian |
| Transport     | scooter | jet-ski    | snowmobile    | trike |

