There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, japanese, pakistani, german
1. the pakistani is on the far left or far right##3
2. the brazilian is somewhere to the right of the german##5
3. the pakistani is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
4. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
5. the brazilian is on the left of the japanese##1
6. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking lemonade and the japanese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | fanta     | lemonade | juice     | almond-milk |
| Nationality   | pakistani | german  | brazilian | japanese        |

