.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, guinea-pig, lizard, chinchilla
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, motorbike, boat, train
1. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person driving the motorbike and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
2. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
3. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet         | lizard   | chinchilla   | hedgehog       | guinea-pig   |
| Transport   | boat | motorbike | van | train |

