.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, corn, trainrot, cauliflower
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, helicopter, tram, scooter
1. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
2. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person driving the tram is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
5. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
6. the person eating pineapple is between the person eating cauliflower and the person driving the train##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | corn     | cauliflower | pineapple | trainrot |
| Transport   | tram | scooter | helicopter      | train        |

 